        "action": "Fund heating in schools and set a legal minimum temperature for classrooms",
        "additional_details": "The Government should increase funding to schools so that they can heat their classrooms to a sensible legal minimum temperature.",
        "background": "The energy crisis is forcing primary schools across England to reduce their heating. This is an appalling situation: small children are spending their days in cold temperatures as they learn.\r\n ",
